# Specialties and Edges

As adventurers grow in power, they develop unique capabilities that set them apart from others of similar training. These specialties represent specialized techniques, natural talents, and hard-won expertise—the small choices that define who you are as a hero.

## What Are Specialties?

When you gain an advance (every 5 XP), you may choose to take a specialty instead of raising a skill or attribute. While skills and attributes measure broad capability, specialties represent focused expertise in narrow areas.

Some specialties can also be earned through play without spending advances—social connections, languages, and unique story rewards can emerge naturally from your adventures.

